<h2>Mateusz Sarello</h2>

<?php if ($langue == 'fr'): ?>
<p>
	Mateusz Sarello est né en 1978, à Varsovie. Il est diplômé de l’Académie de la Photographie de Varsovie. Il est membre de l’agence Images Napo. Il est l’auteur du livre «Swell», qui a été sélectionné comme finaliste pour le Prix du meilleur livre photographique au Pictures of the Year International de 2014. Il a remporté le 3e prix aux International Photography Awards de 2013 et a été choisi par Photo-Eye parmi la liste «des meilleurs livres de 2013”. Ses prix et distinctions comprennent le Center Santa Fe Awards, les prix de l’exposition Objectif Culture, la bourse de la Fondation Lucie, la bourse FotoVisura, la Photolucida Critical Mass, le PDN Photo Annual et les International Awards de la FotoWeek DC.
</p>
<?php endif; ?>

<?php if ($langue == 'en'): ?>
<p>
	Mateusz Sarello was born in 1978 in Warsaw. He is a graduate from the Academy of Photography of Warsaw. He is a member of the Napo Images agency. He is the author of «Swell», a book which was chosen as a finalist in the Best Photography Book Award at the 2014 Pictures of the Year International, he has won the 3rd prize at the International Photography Awards in 2013 and was chosen by Photo-Eye among the «Best Books of 2013» list. His awards and distinctions include the Center Santa Fe Awards, the Lens Culture Exposure Awards, the Lucie Foundation Scholarship, the FotoVisura Grant, the Photolucida Critical Mass, the PDN Photo Annual and the FotoWeekDC International Awards.
</p>
